454 void aciBitmapMenuItem::load(void)
455 {
456  XStream fh;
457  short sx,sy,s;
458  if(!fname) return;
459 
460  if(!(flags & BMI_DATA_LOADED)){
461  fh.open(fname,XS_IN);
462  fh > sx > sy > s;
463 
464  SizeX = sx;
465  SizeY = sy;
466  numStates = s;
467 
468  data = new unsigned char[SizeX * SizeY * numStates];
469  fh.read(data,SizeX * SizeY * numStates);
470  fh.close();
471 
472  flags |= BMI_DATA_LOADED;
473  switch(ID){
474  case BMENU_ITEM_ROT:
475  curState = iGetOptionValue(iCAMERA_TURN);
476  break;
477  case BMENU_ITEM_ZOOM:
478  curState = iGetOptionValue(iCAMERA_SCALE);
479  break;
480  case BMENU_ITEM_PERSP:
481  curState = iGetOptionValue(iCAMERA_SLOPE);
482  break;
483  }
484  }
485 }
486 
487 void aciBitmapMenuItem::free(void)
488 {
489  if(flags & BMI_DATA_LOADED){
490  delete[] data;
491  flags ^= BMI_DATA_LOADED;
492  }
493 }

553 void aciBitmapMenu::build_pict(void)
554 {
555  aciBitmapMenuItem* p = (aciBitmapMenuItem*)items -> last;
556  memset(pictBuf,aciCurColorScheme[ACI_BACK_COL],SizeX * SizeY);
557  while(p){
558  p -> redraw(SizeX,SizeY,pictBuf);
559  p = (aciBitmapMenuItem*)p -> prev;
560  }
561  flags &= ~BM_REBUILD;
562 }

564 void aciBitmapMenu::redraw(int x,int y,int sx,int sy)
565 {
566  int dx,dy;
567 
568  if(!pictBuf) return;
569 
570  dx = (sx - SizeX)/2;
571  dy = (sy - SizeY)/2;
572 
573  if(flags & BM_REBUILD) build_pict();
574  XGR_PutSpr(x + dx,y + dy,SizeX,SizeY,pictBuf,XGR_BLACK_FON);
575 }

593 void aciFont::load(char* fname)
594 {
595  short sx,sy,sz;
596  XStream fh(fname,XS_IN);
597  fh > sx > sy > sz;
598  SizeX = sx;
599  SizeY = sy;
600  Size = sz;
601 
602  data = new unsigned char[SizeX * SizeY * Size];
603  fh.read(data,SizeX * SizeY * Size);
604  fh.close();
605 }
606 
607 void aciFont::calc_offs(void)
608 {
609  int i,j,s,offs = 0;
610  int align_left,align_right,fl,fr;
611  unsigned char* p = data;
612 
613  LeftOffs = new char[Size];
614  RightOffs = new char[Size];
615 
616  for(s = 0; s < Size; s ++){
617  offs = SizeX * SizeY * s;
618  align_left = align_right = 3;
619  for(i = 0; i < SizeY; i ++){
620  fl = fr = 0;
621  for(j = 0; j < SizeX - 1; j ++){
622  if(flags & ACI_RANGE_FONT){
623  if(!fl && p[offs + j] && j < align_left){
624  align_left = j;
625  fl = 1;
626  }
627  if(!fr && p[offs + SizeX - j - 1] && j < align_right){
628  align_right = j;
629  fr = 1;
630  }
631  }
632  else {
633  if(!fl && p[offs + j] == 1 && j < align_left){
634  align_left = j;
635  fl = 1;
636  }
637  if(!fr && p[offs + SizeX - j - 1] == 1 && j < align_right){
638  align_right = j;
639  fr = 1;
640  }
641  }
642  }
643  offs += SizeX;
644  }
645  if(s != ' '){
646  LeftOffs[s] = align_left;
647  RightOffs[s] = align_right;
648  }
649  else {
650  if(SizeX < 8){
651  LeftOffs[s] = 1;
652  RightOffs[s] = 1;
653  }
654  else {
655  LeftOffs[s] = 3;
656  RightOffs[s] = 3;
657  }
658  }
659  }
660 }
661 #endif
662 
663 aciWorldMap::aciWorldMap(void)
664 {
665  int i;
666  redraw_buf = NULL;
667  ShapeSizeX = NULL;
668  ShapeSizeY = NULL;
669 
670  shapes = NULL;
671 
672  flags = WMAP_REBUILD_PIC;
673 
674  world_list = new iList;
675 
676  shape_files = new char*[3];
677  for(i = 0; i < 3; i ++) {
678  shape_files[i] = NULL;
679  }
680 
681  ShapeOffsX = new short[3];
682  ShapeOffsY = new short[3];
683 
684  world_ids = new signed char[AS_MAX_WORLD];
685 
686  for(i = 0; i < 3; i ++)
687  ShapeOffsX[i] = ShapeOffsY[i] = 0;
688 
689  world_ptr = new aciWorldInfo*[AS_MAX_WORLD];
690 }
691 
692 aciWorldMap::~aciWorldMap(void)
693 {
694  int i;
695  aciWorldInfo* p,*p1;
696 
697  delete[] ShapeOffsX;
698  delete[] ShapeOffsY;
699 
700  if(redraw_buf) {
701  delete[] redraw_buf;
702  }
703 
704  delete[] world_ids;
705 
706  if(shapes){
707  for(i = 0; i < AS_NUM_WORLD_SHAPES; i ++)
708  delete[] shapes[i];
709  delete[] shapes;
710  }
711  if(ShapeSizeX){
712  delete[] ShapeSizeX;
713  }
714  if(ShapeSizeY){
715  delete[] ShapeSizeY;
716  }
717 
718  for(i = 0; i < 3; i ++) {
719  if(shape_files[i]) {
720  delete[] shape_files[i];
721  }
722  }
723  delete[] shape_files;
724 
725  p = (aciWorldInfo*)world_list -> last;
726  while(p){
727  p1 = (aciWorldInfo*)p -> prev;
728  delete p;
729  p = p1;
730  }
731  delete world_list;
732 
733  delete[] world_ptr;
734 }

736 int aciWorldMap::world_key(int id)
737 {
738  int i;
739  aciWorldInfo* p,*p1;
740 
741  p1 = NULL;
742  p = (aciWorldInfo*)world_list -> last;
743  while(p){
744  if(p -> links[id]) return 1;
745  if(p -> ID == id) p1 = p;
746  p = (aciWorldInfo*)p -> prev;
747  }
748  if(p1){
749  for(i = 0; i < AS_MAX_WORLD; i ++)
750  if(p1 -> links[i]) return 1;
751  }
752  return 0;
753 }

892 void aciLocationInfo::prepare(void)
893 {
894  int i;
895  iScreen* scr;
896  if(!objIDs[ACI_SHOP_SCREEN_ID]){
897  for(i = 0; i < ACI_NUM_OBJECTS; i ++)
898  objList[i] = NULL;
899  }
900  else {
901  scr = (iScreen*)iScrDisp -> get_object(objIDs[ACI_SHOP_SCREEN_ID]);
902  for(i = 0; i < ACI_NUM_OBJECTS; i ++){
903  if(objIDs[i]){
904  objList[i] = scr -> get_object(objIDs[i]);
905  }
906  else {
907  objList[i] = NULL;
908  }
909  }
910  }
911  scr = (iScreen*)iScrDisp -> get_object(screenID);
912  if(!scr) ErrH.Abort("Escave screen not found...");
913  for(i = 0; i < ACI_NUM_S_OBJECTS; i ++){
914  if(s_objIDs[i]){
915  s_objList[i] = scr -> get_object(s_objIDs[i]);
916  }
917  else {
918  s_objList[i] = NULL;
919  }
920  }
921 }

930  index ++;
931  }
932  }
933  }

936 void aciLocationInfo::init_map_data(void)
937 {

939  unsigned char* data;
940 
941  XStream fh;
942 
943  iListElement* p = mapData -> last;
944 
945  while(p){
946  if(p -> ID_ptr.size()){
947  fh.open(p->ID_ptr.c_str(),XS_IN);
948  fh > sx > sy > num > x > y;
949  data = new unsigned char[sx * sy * num];
950  fh.read(data,sx * sy * num);
951  fh.close();
952 
953  put_fon(x,y,sx,sy,data);
954  put_attr_fon(x,y,sx,sy,data + sx * sy);
955 // iregRender(x,y,x + sx,y + sy);
956 
957  delete[] data;
958  }
959  p = p -> prev;
960  }
961 }

1052 void bmlObject::load(const char* fname,int bmp)
1053 {
1054  if(!fname)
1055  fname = name;
1056 
1057  if(!fname) return;
1058 
1059  if(flags & BML_FRAMES_LOADED) free();
1060 
1061  XStream fh(fname,XS_IN);
1062  if(bmp)
1063  flags |= BMP_FLAG;
1064 
1065  if(!(flags & BMP_FLAG) && !(flags & BG_FLAG)){
1066  if(!(flags & BML_NO_OFFSETS))
1067  fh > SizeX > SizeY > Size > OffsX > OffsY;
1068  else
1069  fh > SizeX > SizeY > Size;
1070  }
1071  else {
1072  if(flags & BMP_FLAG){
1073  fh > SizeX > SizeY;
1074  Size = 1;
1075  }
1076  if(flags & BG_FLAG){
1077  Size = 1;
1078  }
1079  }
1080  frames = new unsigned char[SizeX * SizeY * Size];
1081  fh.read(frames,SizeX * SizeY * Size);
1082  fh.close();
1083 
1084  flags |= BML_FRAMES_LOADED;
1085 }
1086 
1087 void bmlObject::load2mem(unsigned char* ptr,char* fname)
1088 {
1089  if(!fname)
1090  fname = name;
1091 
1092  if(!fname) return;
1093 
1094  //std::cout<<"bmlObject::load2mem "<<fname<<std::endl;
1095  XStream fh(fname,XS_IN);
1096 
1097  if(!(flags & BMP_FLAG) && !(flags & BG_FLAG)){
1098  fh > SizeX > SizeY > Size > OffsX > OffsY;
1099  }
1100  else {
1101  if(flags & BMP_FLAG){
1102  fh > SizeX > SizeY;
1103  Size = 1;
1104  }
1105  if(flags & BG_FLAG){
1106  Size = 1;
1107  }
1108  }
1109  fh.read(ptr,SizeX * SizeY * Size);
1110  fh.close();
1111 }

1167 void ibsObject::load(char* fname)

1172

1174  XBuffer XBuf;
1175  XBuf < fname < ".xbm";

1179  fh.read(image,ImageSize);
1180  fh.close();

1184 
1185  CenterX = PosX + SideX;
1186  CenterY = PosY + SideY;

1647  }

1661  ox = (dx - aScrFonts32[font] -> SizeX) >> 1;
1662  }
1663  else {

1665  ox = (dx - aScrFonts[font] -> SizeX) >> 1;
1666  }

1676  }

1693  x += dx - 1;
1694  }

1700  else

1702  x += dx - 1;
1703  }

1716 void invItem::redraw(int x,int y,int drop_mode,int flush_mode)
1717 {
1718  int dx,dy,col = 0,mx,my;
1719  unsigned char* buf;
1720 
1721  mx = MatrixX * aCellSize + (aCellSize >> 1);
1722  if(MatrixY & 0x01) mx += (aCellSize >> 1);
1723 
1724  my = MatrixY * (aCellSize - (aCellSize >> 2)) + (aCellSize >> 1);
1725 
1726  dx = mx - ShapeCenterX + (ShapeSizeX >> 1) - (ScreenSizeX >> 1);
1727  dy = my - ShapeCenterY + (ShapeSizeY >> 1) - (ScreenSizeY >> 1);
1728 
1729  if(aciBufRedrawFlag){
1730  put_buf2col(800 + x + dx,y + dy,ScreenSizeX,ScreenSizeY,(unsigned char*)frame,300,0);
1731 // put_map(800 + x + dx,y + dy,ScreenSizeX,ScreenSizeY);
1732  }
1733  else {
1734  XGR_PutSpr(x + dx,y + dy,ScreenSizeX,ScreenSizeY,frame,XGR_HIDDEN_FON);
1735 
1736  if(flush_mode)
1737  XGR_Flush(x + dx,y + dy,ScreenSizeX,ScreenSizeY);
1738  }
1739 
1740  if(drop_mode){
1741  switch(slotType){
1742  case -1:
1743  col = aciCurColorScheme[INV_NUM_ITM_COL];
1744  break;
1745  case AS_WEAPON_SLOT:
1746  col = aciCurColorScheme[INV_NUM_WPN_COL];
1747  break;
1748  case AS_TWEAPON_SLOT:
1749  col = aciCurColorScheme[INV_NUM_TWPN_COL];
1750  break;
1751  case AS_DEVICE_SLOT:
1752  col = aciCurColorScheme[INV_NUM_DVC_COL];
1753  break;
1754  }
1755  dx = mx + ShapeX[NumIndex] * aCellSize - (aCellSize >> 1);
1756  dy = my + ShapeY[NumIndex] * (aCellSize - (aCellSize >> 2)) - (aCellSize >> 1);
1757 
1758  if(ShapeY[NumIndex] & 0x01) dx += (aCellSize >> 1);
1759 
1760  buf = new unsigned char[aCellSize * aCellSize];
1761  memset(buf,0,aCellSize * aCellSize);
1762  aPutNum(aCellSize/2 - aScrFonts[INV_FONT] -> SizeX/2,aCellSize/2 - aScrFonts[INV_FONT] -> SizeY/2,INV_FONT,col,dropCount,aCellSize,buf,1);
1763 
1764  if(aciBufRedrawFlag){
1765  put_buf2col(800 + x + dx,y + dy,aCellSize,aCellSize,buf,300,0);
1766 // put_map(800 + x + dx,y + dy,aCellSize,aCellSize);
1767  }
1768  else {
1769  XGR_PutSpr(x + dx,y + dy,aCellSize,aCellSize,buf,XGR_HIDDEN_FON);
1770 
1771  if(flush_mode)
1772  XGR_Flush(x + dx,y + dy,aCellSize,aCellSize);
1773  }
1774 
1775  delete[] buf;
1776  }
1777  if(aciBufRedrawFlag && flush_mode){
1778  dx = mx - ShapeCenterX + (ShapeSizeX >> 1) - (ScreenSizeX >> 1);
1779  dy = my - ShapeCenterY + (ShapeSizeY >> 1) - (ScreenSizeY >> 1);
1780  put_map(800 + x + dx,y + dy,ScreenSizeX,ScreenSizeY);
1781  }
1782 #ifdef _ACI_BOUND_TEST_
1783  col = aciCurColorScheme[INV_NUM_ITM_COL];
1784 
1785  dx = mx - ShapeCenterX;
1786  dy = my - ShapeCenterY;
1787  XGR_Rectangle(x + dx,y + dy,ShapeSizeX,ShapeSizeY,col,col,XGR_OUTLINED);
1788  XGR_Rectangle(x + dx + ShapeCenterX - 1,y + dy + ShapeCenterY - 1,3,3,col,col,XGR_FILLED);
1789 #endif
1790 }

2046 int invMatrix::check_fit(int x,int y,invItem* p)
2047 {
2048  int i,offs = 0;
2049 
2050  int ix = x,iy = y,dl = p -> ShapeLen,tp = p -> slotType;
2051  int* dx = p -> ShapeX;
2052  int* dy = p -> ShapeY;
2053 
2054  for(i = 0; i < dl; i ++){
2055  ix = x + dx[i];
2056  iy = y + dy[i];
2057 
2058  if((y & 0x01) && (dy[i] & 0x01))
2059  ix ++;
2060 
2061  if(ix < 0 || iy < 0 || ix >= SizeX || iy >= SizeY)
2062  return 0;
2063 
2064  offs = ix + iy * SizeX;
2065 
2066  if(matrix[offs] -> type == AS_NO_CELL || (tp != matrix[offs] -> slotType && matrix[offs] -> slotType != -1) || (matrix[offs] -> flags & AS_BUSY_CELL))
2067  return 0;
2068  }
2069  return 1;
2070 }

2072 int invMatrix::auto_put_item(invItem* p)
2073 {
2074  int x,y,offs = 0;
2075  for(y = 0; y < SizeY; y ++){
2076  for(x = 0; x < SizeX; x ++){
2077  if(!(p -> flags & INV_ITEM_NO_ACTIVATE) || p -> slotType != matrix[offs] -> slotType){
2078  if(put_item(x,y,p))
2079  return 1;
2080  }
2081  offs ++;
2082  }
2083  }
2084  return 0;
2085 }

2087 int invMatrix::put_item(int x,int y,invItem* p,int mode)
2088 {
2089  int i,offs = 0,ix,iy;
2090  if(!check_fit(x,y,p))
2091  return 0;
2092 
2093  p -> MatrixX = x;
2094  p -> MatrixY = y;
2095 
2096  ix = x;
2097  iy = y;
2098 
2099  for(i = 0; i < p -> ShapeLen; i ++){
2100  ix = x + p -> ShapeX[i];
2101  iy = y + p -> ShapeY[i];
2102 
2103  if((y & 0x01) && (p -> ShapeY[i] & 0x01))
2104  ix ++;
2105 
2106  offs = ix + iy * SizeX;
2107  matrix[offs] -> put_item(p);
2108  }
2109 
2110  items -> connect((iListElement*)p);
2111  if(!mode)
2112  p -> dropCount = items -> Size;
2113  if(p -> slotType != -1)
2114  fill(p);
2115  return 1;
2116 }

2138 void invMatrix::fill(invItem* p)
2139 {
2140  int x,y,flag = 1,index;
2141  invMatrixCell* ic,*ic1;
2142 
2143  while(flag){
2144  index = 0;
2145  flag = 0;
2146  for(y = 0; y < SizeY; y ++){
2147  for(x = 0; x < SizeX; x ++){
2148  ic = matrix[index];
2149  if(ic -> flags & AS_BUSY_CELL && ic -> item == p && ic -> slotType != -1){
2150  if(x){
2151  ic1 = matrix[index - 1];
2152  if(ic1 -> slotNumber == ic -> slotNumber && !(ic1 -> flags & AS_BUSY_CELL)){
2153  flag = 1;
2154  ic1 -> put_item(p);
2155  }
2156  }
2157  if(x < SizeX - 1){
2158  ic1 = matrix[index + 1];
2159  if(ic1 -> slotNumber == ic -> slotNumber && !(ic1 -> flags & AS_BUSY_CELL)){
2160  flag = 1;
2161  ic1 -> put_item(p);
2162  }
2163  }
2164  if(y){
2165  ic1 = matrix[index - SizeX];
2166  if(ic1 -> slotNumber == ic -> slotNumber && !(ic1 -> flags & AS_BUSY_CELL)){
2167  flag = 1;
2168  ic1 -> put_item(p);
2169  }
2170  }
2171  if(y < SizeY - SizeX){
2172  ic1 = matrix[index + SizeX];
2173  if(ic1 -> slotNumber == ic -> slotNumber && !(ic1 -> flags & AS_BUSY_CELL)){
2174  flag = 1;
2175  ic1 -> put_item(p);
2176  }
2177  }
2178  }
2179  index ++;
2180  }
2181  }
2182  }
2183 }

2185 void invMatrix::remove_item(invItem* p,int mode)
2186 {
2187  int i, j, index = 0;
2188  invItem* itm;
2189 
2190  for(i = 0; i < SizeY; i ++){
2191  for(j = 0; j < SizeX; j ++){
2192  if(matrix[index] -> flags & AS_BUSY_CELL && matrix[index] -> item == p)
2193  matrix[index] -> remove_item();
2194  index ++;
2195  }
2196  }
2197  items -> dconnect((iListElement*)p);
2198 
2199  if(!mode){
2200  itm = (invItem*)items -> last;
2201  while(itm){
2202  if(itm -> dropCount > p -> dropCount)
2203  itm -> dropCount --;
2204  itm = (invItem*)itm -> prev;
2205  }
2206  }
2207 }

2218 invItem* invMatrix::get_area_item(int x,int y,invItem* it)
2219 {
2220  int i,index,ix,iy;
2221  invItem* p = NULL;
2222 
2223  for(i = 0; i < it -> ShapeLen; i ++){
2224  ix = x + it -> ShapeX[i];
2225  iy = y + it -> ShapeY[i];
2226 
2227  if((y & 0x01) && (it -> ShapeY[i] & 0x01))
2228  ix ++;
2229 
2230  if(ix < 0 || ix >= SizeX || iy < 0 || iy >= SizeY)
2231  return NULL;
2232 
2233  index = ix + iy * SizeX;

2716 void invMatrix::redraw_matrix(void)
2717 {
2718  int i,j,x0,y0,x = 0,y = 0,col = 0,col1 = 0,index = 0;
2719 
2720  int dx = aCellSize;
2721  int dx2 = aCellSize >> 1;
2722  int dx4 = aCellSize >> 2;
2723 
2724  int ssx = ScreenSizeX + aCellSize;
2725  int ssy = ScreenSizeY + aCellSize;
2726  int ssz = ssx * ssy;
2727 
2728  unsigned char* p,*scr_buf;
2729  p = new unsigned char[(dx + 1) * (dx + 1)];
2730 
2731  if(aciBufRedrawFlag){
2732  scr_buf = new unsigned char[ssz];
2733  memset(scr_buf,0,ssz);
2734  }
2735 
2736  for(i = 0; i < SizeY; i ++){
2737  if(i & 0x01){
2738  x += dx2;
2739  }
2740  for(j = 0; j < SizeX; j ++){
2741  if(matrix[index] -> type && !(matrix[index] -> flags & AS_BUSY_CELL)){
2742  memcpy(p,aCellFrame,(dx + 1) * (dx + 1));
2743 
2744  if(matrix[index] -> slotType == -1){
2745  col = aciCurColorScheme[INV_FLOOR_COL_ITM];
2746  col1 = aciCurColorScheme[INV_CELL_COL_ITM];
2747  }
2748  else {
2749  col = aciCurColorScheme[matrix[index] -> slotType * 4 + INV_FLOOR_COL_ITM];
2750  col1 = aciCurColorScheme[matrix[index] -> slotType * 4 + INV_CELL_COL_ITM];
2751  }
2752 
2753  swap_buf_col(1,col1,dx + 1,dx + 1,p);
2754  swap_buf_col(2,col,dx + 1,dx + 1,p);
2755 
2756  x0 = x + ScreenX;
2757  y0 = y + ScreenY;
2758 
2759  if(aciBufRedrawFlag)
2760  mem_putspr_h(x,y,dx + 1,dx + 1,ssx,ssy,p,scr_buf);
2761  else
2762  XGR_PutSpr(x0,y0,dx + 1,dx + 1,p,XGR_HIDDEN_FON);
2763  }
2764  x += aCellSize;
2765  index ++;
2766  }
2767  x = 0;
2768  y += aCellSize - dx4;
2769  }
2770 
2771  x = 0;
2772  y = 0;
2773  index = 0;
2774 
2775  for(i = 0; i < SizeY; i ++){
2776  if(i & 0x01){
2777  x += dx2;
2778  }
2779  for(j = 0; j < SizeX; j ++){
2780  if(matrix[index] -> type && (matrix[index] -> flags & AS_BUSY_CELL)){
2781  memcpy(p,aCellFrame,(dx + 1) * (dx + 1));
2782 
2783  if(matrix[index] -> slotType == -1){
2784  col = aciCurColorScheme[INV_BFLOOR_COL_ITM];
2785  col1 = aciCurColorScheme[INV_BCELL_COL_ITM];
2786  }
2787  else {
2788  col = aciCurColorScheme[matrix[index] -> slotType * 4 + INV_BFLOOR_COL_ITM];
2789  col1 = aciCurColorScheme[matrix[index] -> slotType * 4 + INV_BCELL_COL_ITM];
2790  }
2791 
2792  swap_buf_col(1,col1,dx + 1,dx + 1,p);
2793  swap_buf_col(2,col,dx + 1,dx + 1,p);
2794 
2795  x0 = x + ScreenX;
2796  y0 = y + ScreenY;
2797 
2798  if(aciBufRedrawFlag)
2799  mem_putspr_h(x,y,dx + 1,dx + 1,ssx,ssy,p,scr_buf);
2800  else
2801  XGR_PutSpr(x0,y0,dx + 1,dx + 1,p,XGR_HIDDEN_FON);
2802  }
2803  x += aCellSize;

4361 void fncMenu::init_objects(void)
4362 {
4363  int i,sx = 0;
4364  fncMenuItem* p;
4365 
4366  p = (fncMenuItem*)items -> first;
4367  for(i = 0; i < items -> Size; i ++){
4368  p -> init();
4369  p -> PosX = (SizeX - p -> SizeX)/2;
4370  if(flags & FM_NO_ALIGN && sx < p -> SizeX) sx = p -> SizeX;
4371  p = (fncMenuItem*)p -> next;
4372  }
4373 
4374  if(flags & FM_NO_ALIGN){
4375  SizeX = sx;
4376  p = (fncMenuItem*)items -> first;
4377  for(i = 0; i < items -> Size; i ++){
4378  p -> PosX = (SizeX - p -> SizeX)/2;
4379  p = (fncMenuItem*)p -> next;
4380  }
4381  }
4382

4444 void fncMenu::redraw(void)
4445 {
4446  int i,b_col,sx,sy;
4447  unsigned char* buf;
4448  fncMenuItem* p = firstItem;
4449  iScreenObject* obj;
4450 
4451  flags &= ~FM_REDRAW;
4452  if(!(flags & FM_ACTIVE)){
4453  if(!curFunction && bml){
4454  bml -> show();
4455  }
4456  else
4457  redraw_fnc(PosX,PosY,SizeX,SizeY,curFunction);
4458  }
4459  else {
4460  init_redraw();
4461 
4462  if(!iScreenOwner){
4463  buf = new unsigned char[SizeX * SizeY];
4464  }
4465  else {
4466  if(!(iScreenOwner -> flags & EL_DATA_LOADED))
4467  return;
4468  obj = (iScreenObject*)iScreenOwner -> owner;
4469  obj -> flags |= OBJ_MUST_REDRAW;
4470  if(!bCol)
4471  obj -> flags |= OBJ_CLEAR_FON;
4472  buf = (unsigned char*)iScreenOwner -> fdata;
4473 
4474  sx = iScreenOwner -> SizeX;
4475  sy = iScreenOwner -> SizeY;
4476  }
4477 
4478  if(!(flags & FM_NO_ALIGN)){
4479  b_col = (bCol == -1) ? aciCurColorScheme[ACI_BACK_COL] : bCol;
4480  memset(buf,b_col,SizeX * SizeY);
4481  }
4482 
4483  if(items -> Size){
4484  if(prefix){
4485  curItem -> redraw_str(SizeX,SizeY,buf,PrefixX,PrefixY,prefix);
4486  if(postfix)
4487  curItem -> redraw_str(SizeX,SizeY,buf,PrefixX + PrefixSX + curItem -> SizeX + FM_PREFIX_DELTA * 2,PrefixY,postfix);
4488  }
4489  if(VItems < items -> Size){
4490  if(flags & FM_RANGE_FONT){
4491  up_obj -> flags |= FM_RANGE_FONT;
4492  down_obj -> flags |= FM_RANGE_FONT;
4493  }
4494  if(!(flags & FM_NO_ALIGN)){
4495  up_obj -> redraw(SizeX,SizeY,buf,up_obj -> PosX + PrefixDelta,up_obj -> PosY);
4496  down_obj -> redraw(SizeX,SizeY,buf,down_obj -> PosX + PrefixDelta,down_obj -> PosY);
4497  }
4498  else {
4499  up_obj -> redraw(sx,sy,buf,up_obj -> PosX + PrefixDelta + PosX,up_obj -> PosY + PosY);
4500  down_obj -> redraw(sx,sy,buf,down_obj -> PosX + PrefixDelta + PosX,down_obj -> PosY + PosY);
4501  }
4502  }
4503  if(!(flags & FM_NO_ALIGN)){
4504  for(i = 0; i < VItems; i ++){
4505  if(p == curItem)
4506  p -> flags |= FM_SELECTED;
4507  else
4508  p -> flags &= ~FM_SELECTED;
4509 
4510  p -> redraw(SizeX,SizeY,buf,p -> PosX + PrefixDelta,p -> PosY);
4511  p = (fncMenuItem*)p -> next;
4512  if(p == firstItem) i = VItems;
4513  }
4514  }
4515  else {
4516  for(i = 0; i < VItems; i ++){
4517  if(p == curItem)
4518  p -> flags |= FM_SELECTED;
4519  else
4520  p -> flags &= ~FM_SELECTED;
4521 
4522  p -> redraw(sx,sy,buf,p -> PosX + PrefixDelta + PosX,p -> PosY + PosY);
4523  p = (fncMenuItem*)p -> next;
4524  if(p == firstItem) i = VItems;
4525  }
4526  }
4527  if(!iScreenOwner){
4528  XGR_PutSpr(PosX,PosY,SizeX,SizeY,buf,XGR_BLACK_FON);
4529  delete[] buf;
4530  }
4531  }
4532  }
4533  if(ibs) ibs -> show();
4534 
4535  if(flags & FM_OFF){
4536  flags &= ~(FM_ACTIVE | FM_OFF);
4537  }
4538 }

4540 void InfoPanel::redraw(void)
4541 {
4542  int i,x,y,fnt,col,col1 = 0,col_sz,tmp1,tmp2;
4543  unsigned char* buf;
4544  iScreenObject* obj;
4545  InfoPanelItem* p = (InfoPanelItem*)items -> first;
4546 
4547  if(!iScreenOwner){
4548  buf = new unsigned char[SizeX * SizeY];
4549  }
4550  else {
4551  if(!(iScreenOwner -> flags & EL_DATA_LOADED))
4552  return;
4553  obj = (iScreenObject*)iScreenOwner -> owner;
4554  obj -> flags |= OBJ_MUST_REDRAW;
4555  if(!bCol)
4556  obj -> flags |= OBJ_CLEAR_FON;
4557  buf = (unsigned char*)iScreenOwner -> fdata;
4558  }
4559 
4560  int b_col = (bCol == -1) ? aciCurColorScheme[ACI_BACK_COL] : bCol;
4561  memset(buf,b_col,SizeX * SizeY);
4562 
4563  if(!(flags & IP_RANGE_FONT))
4564  y = OffsY + ((SizeY - items -> Size * (aScrFonts[font] -> SizeY + vSpace)) >> 1);
4565  else
4566  y = OffsY + ((SizeY - items -> Size * (aScrFonts32[font] -> SizeY + vSpace)) >> 1);
4567 
4568  for(i = 0; i < items -> Size; i ++){
4569  if(p -> font == -1)
4570  fnt = font;
4571  else
4572  fnt = p -> font;
4573 
4574 #ifdef _ACI_BML_FONTS_
4575  col1 = (aciCurColorScheme[FM_SELECT_BORDER_COL] << 8) | aciCurColorScheme[FM_SELECT_COL];
4576  if(p -> color == -1){
4577  if(!(flags & IP_RANGE_FONT)){
4578  col = (aciCurColorScheme[FM_UNSELECT_BORDER_COL] << 8) | aciCurColorScheme[FM_UNSELECT_COL];
4579  col |= (col1 << 16);
4580  }
4581  else {
4582  col = (aciCurColorScheme[FM_SELECT_START] << 16) | aciCurColorScheme[FM_UNSELECT_START];
4583  col_sz = (aciCurColorScheme[FM_SELECT_SIZE] << 16) | aciCurColorScheme[FM_UNSELECT_SIZE];
4584  }
4585  }
4586  else {
4587  if(!(flags & IP_RANGE_FONT)){
4588  col = col1;
4589  }
4590  else {
4591  if(p -> color & (~0xFFFF)){
4592  tmp1 = p -> color & 0xFF;
4593  tmp2 = (p -> color >> 8) & 0xFF;
4594  col = (tmp2 << 16) | tmp1;
4595 
4596  tmp1 = (p -> color >> 16) & 0xFF;
4597  tmp2 = (p -> color >> 24) & 0xFF;
4598  col_sz = (tmp2 << 16) | tmp1;
4599  }
4600  else {
4601  col = (aciCurColorScheme[FM_SELECT_START] << 16) | aciCurColorScheme[FM_SELECT_START];
4602  col_sz = (aciCurColorScheme[FM_SELECT_SIZE] << 16) | aciCurColorScheme[FM_SELECT_SIZE];
4603  }
4604  }
4605  }
4606 #else
4607  if(p -> color == -1)
4608  col = aciCurColorScheme[FM_UNSELECT_COL];
4609  else
4610  col = aciCurColorScheme[FM_SELECT_COL];
4611 #endif
4612 
4613  if(flags & IP_NO_ALIGN){
4614  x = OffsX;
4615  }
4616  else {
4617  if(!(flags & IP_RANGE_FONT))
4618  x = OffsX + ((SizeX - aStrLen((unsigned char*)p->ID_ptr.c_str(), font,hSpace)) >> 1);
4619  else
4620  x = OffsX + ((SizeX - aStrLen32((void*)p->ID_ptr.c_str(), font,hSpace)) >> 1);
4621  }
4622  if(y < 0) ErrH.Abort("InfoPanel overflow...");
4623  if(!(flags & IP_RANGE_FONT)){
4624  aPutStr(x,y,fnt,col,(unsigned char*)p->ID_ptr.c_str(),SizeX,buf,hSpace);
4625  }
4626  else {
4627  aPutStr32(x,y,fnt,col,col_sz, (void*)p->ID_ptr.c_str(),SizeX,buf,hSpace);
4628  }
4629 
4630  if(!(flags & IP_RANGE_FONT))
4631  y += aScrFonts[font] -> SizeY + vSpace;
4632  else
4633  y += aScrFonts32[font] -> SizeY + vSpace;
4634 
4635  p = (InfoPanelItem*)p -> next;
4636  }
4637  if(!iScreenOwner){
4638  XGR_PutSpr(PosX,PosY,SizeX,SizeY,buf,XGR_BLACK_FON);
4639  delete[] buf;
4640  }
4641 
4642  if(ibs) ibs -> show();
4643  flags &= ~IP_REDRAW;
4644 }

5014  if(!(m -> flags & FM_HIDDEN) && m -> check_xy(iMouseX,iMouseY)){
5015  if(m -> flags & FM_ACTIVE){
5016  m -> change(iMouseX,iMouseY,1);
5017  }
5018  }
5019  m = (fncMenu*)m -> prev;
5020  }
5021  if(iMouseLPressFlag){
5022  if(qMenu && qMenu -> flags & FMC_DATA_INIT && qMenu -> check_xy(iMouseX,iMouseY) && qMenu -> check_xy(iMousePrevX,iMousePrevY)){
5023  qMenu -> shift((iMouseX - iMousePrevX) * 4);
5024  }
5025  }
5026  }
5027  if(flags & aMS_PRESS){
5028  if(flags & aMS_LEFT_PRESS){
5029  if(qMenu && qMenu -> flags & FMC_DATA_INIT){
5030  qMenu -> key_trap(iMouseX,iMouseY);
5031  }
5032  m = (fncMenu*)i_menuList -> last;
5033  while(m){
5034  if(m -> check_xy(iMouseX,iMouseY)){
5035  if(m -> flags & FM_ACTIVE){
5036  m -> change(iMouseX,iMouseY);
5037  SOUND_SELECT();
5038  }
5039  }
5040  m = (fncMenu*)m -> prev;
5041  }
5042  flags &= ~aMS_LEFT_PRESS;
5043  }
5044  }
5045  }
5046 }

5048 void actIntDispatcher::iKeyTrap(int cd)
5049 {
5050  fncMenu* m;
5051  if(!NetworkON) aciCHandler(cd);
5052  if(!(flags & AS_ISCREEN_INV_MODE)){
5053  m = (fncMenu*)i_menuList -> last;
5054  while(m){
5055  if(m -> flags & FM_LOCATION_MENU && m -> flags & FM_ACTIVE && m -> up_key -> check(cd)){
5056  m -> step_up();
5057  m -> set_redraw();
5058  SOUND_SELECT();
5059  }
5060  if(m -> flags & FM_ACTIVE && m -> down_key -> check(cd)){
5061  m -> step_down();
5062  m -> set_redraw();
5063  SOUND_SELECT();
5064  }
5065  m = (fncMenu*)m -> prev;
5066  }
5067  }

5070 void actIntDispatcher::send_event(int cd,int dt,actintItemData* p)

5078  else
5079  events -> put(cd,dt,p);
5080 }

5518 actEventHeap::actEventHeap(void)
5519 {
5520  int i;
5521  table = new actEvent*[AS_MAX_EVENT];
5522  mem_heap = new char[AS_MAX_EVENT * sizeof(actEvent)];
5523  for(i = 0; i < AS_MAX_EVENT; i ++){
5524  table[i] = (actEvent*)(mem_heap + sizeof(actEvent) * i);
5525  }
5526  clear();
5527 }

5535 void actEventHeap::put(int cd,int dt,actintItemData* p)
5536 {
5537  if(size < AS_MAX_EVENT){
5538  table[last_index] -> code = cd;
5539  table[last_index] -> data = dt;
5540  table[last_index] -> ptr = p;
5541 
5542  last_index ++;
5543  if(last_index >= AS_MAX_EVENT)
5544  last_index = 0;
5545  size ++;
5546  }
5547  else
5548  ErrH.Abort("Event buffer overflow...");
5549 }
5550 
5551 actEvent* actEventHeap::get(void)
5552 {
5553  actEvent* p;
5554  if(size){
5555  p = table[first_index];
5556 
5557  first_index ++;
5558  if(first_index >= AS_MAX_EVENT)
5559  first_index = 0;
5560 
5561  size --;
5562  return p;
5563  }
5564  return NULL;
5565 }

5568 {

5570  first_index = 0;
5571  last_index = 0;
5572 }

5596 void actIntDispatcher::init_menus(void)
5597 {
5598  fncMenu* m,*m1;
5599  fncMenuItem* p,*p1;
5600  m = (fncMenu*)menuList -> last;
5601  while(m){
5602  if(!(m -> flags & FM_SUBMENU)){
5603  p = (fncMenuItem*)m -> inactive_items -> last;
5604  while(p){
5605  p1 = (fncMenuItem*)p -> prev;
5606  m -> inactive_items -> dconnect((iListElement*)p);
5607  m -> items -> connect((iListElement*)p);
5608  p = p1;
5609  }
5610  m -> curItem = m -> get_fnc_item(m -> curFunction);
5611  if(m -> VItems < m -> items -> Size)
5612  m -> firstItem = m -> curItem;
5613  else
5614  m -> firstItem = (fncMenuItem*)m -> items -> first;
5615  m -> trigger = get_button(m -> trigger_code);
5616  }
5617  m = (fncMenu*)m -> prev;
5618  }
5619 
5620  m = (fncMenu*)menuList -> last;
5621  while(m){
5622  if(!(m -> flags & FM_SUBMENU)){
5623  p = (fncMenuItem*)m -> items -> last;
5624  while(p){
5625  p1 = (fncMenuItem*)p -> prev;
5626  m1 = (fncMenu*)menuList -> last;
5627  while(m1){
5628  if(!(m1 -> flags & FM_SUBMENU)){
5629  if(m1 != m && m1 -> curFunction && m1 -> curFunction == p -> fnc_code){
5630  if(m -> curItem == p){
5631  m -> curItem = (fncMenuItem*)p -> next;
5632  m -> curFunction = m -> curItem -> fnc_code;
5633  }
5634  m -> items -> dconnect((iListElement*)p);
5635  m -> inactive_items -> connect((iListElement*)p);
5636  m1 = NULL;
5637  }
5638  else
5639  m1 = (fncMenu*)m1 -> prev;
5640  }
5641  else
5642  m1 = (fncMenu*)m1 -> prev;
5643  }
5644  p = p1;
5645  }
5646  m -> sort();
5647  m -> curItem = m -> get_fnc_item(m -> curFunction);
5648  if(m -> VItems < m -> items -> Size)
5649  m -> firstItem = m -> curItem;
5650  else
5651  m -> firstItem = (fncMenuItem*)m -> items -> first;
5652 
5653  if(m -> flags & FM_ACTIVE) m -> set_redraw();
5654  }
5655  m = (fncMenu*)m -> prev;
5656  }
5657 }

5663  if(p -> fnc_code == fnc)
5664  return p;

5666  }
5667  return NULL;

5689 }

5691 void fncMenu::step_up(void)
5692 {
5693  if(curItem -> prev){
5694  curItem = (fncMenuItem*)curItem -> prev;
5695  }
5696  else {
5697  curItem = (fncMenuItem*)items -> last;
5698  }
5699 
5700  init_redraw();
5701  while(!(curItem -> flags & FM_VISIBLE)){
5702  firstItem = (fncMenuItem*)firstItem -> prev;
5703  if(!firstItem) firstItem = (fncMenuItem*)items -> last;
5704  init_redraw();
5705  }
5706  if(trigger)
5707  trigger -> curCount = 0;
5708 
5709  curFunction = curItem -> fnc_code;
5710 }
5711 
5712 void fncMenu::step_down(void)
5713 {
5714  curItem = (fncMenuItem*)curItem -> next;
5715  init_redraw();
5716  while(!(curItem -> flags & FM_VISIBLE)){
5717  firstItem = (fncMenuItem*)firstItem -> next;
5718  init_redraw();
5719  }
5720  if(trigger)
5721  trigger -> curCount = 0;
5722 
5723  curFunction = curItem -> fnc_code;
5724 }

5751 void fncMenu::init_redraw(void)
5752 {
5753  int i,dy = 0,min_y,max_y,max_sy;
5754  fncMenuItem* p;
5755 
5756  p = (fncMenuItem*)items -> last;
5757  if(!p) return;
5758  while(p){
5759  p -> flags &= ~FM_VISIBLE;
5760  p = (fncMenuItem*)p -> prev;
5761  }
5762 
5763  if(!prefix){
5764  p = firstItem;
5765  for(i = 0; i < VItems; i ++){
5766  p -> flags |= FM_VISIBLE;
5767  p -> PosY = dy;
5768  dy += p -> SizeY + p -> space;
5769  p = (fncMenuItem*)p -> next;
5770  if(p == firstItem) i = VItems;
5771  }
5772  itemY = (SizeY - dy) / 2;
5773 
5774  p = firstItem;
5775  for(i = 0; i < VItems; i ++){
5776  p -> PosY += itemY;
5777  p = (fncMenuItem*)p -> next;
5778  if(p == firstItem) i = VItems;
5779  }
5780  }
5781  else {
5782  curItem -> PosY = PrefixY;
5783  curItem -> flags |= FM_VISIBLE;
5784  if(items -> Size > 2){
5785  if(curItem -> prev)
5786  p = (fncMenuItem*)curItem -> prev;
5787  else
5788  p = (fncMenuItem*)items -> last;
5789 
5790  p -> PosY = curItem -> PosY - (p -> space + p -> SizeY);
5791  p -> flags |= FM_VISIBLE;
5792 
5793  firstItem = p;
5794  p = (fncMenuItem*)curItem -> next;
5795  p -> PosY = curItem -> PosY + (curItem -> space + curItem -> SizeY);
5796  p -> flags |= FM_VISIBLE;
5797  }
5798  else {
5799  if(items -> Size == 2){
5800  firstItem = curItem;
5801  p = (fncMenuItem*)curItem -> next;
5802  p -> PosY = curItem -> PosY + (curItem -> space + curItem -> SizeY);
5803  p -> flags |= FM_VISIBLE;
5804  }
5805  }
5806  }
5807  p = firstItem;
5808  min_y = max_y = p -> PosY;
5809  max_sy = p -> SizeY;
5810  for(i = 0; i < VItems; i ++){
5811  if(min_y > p -> PosY)
5812  min_y = p -> PosY;
5813  if(max_y < p -> PosY){
5814  max_y = p -> PosY;
5815  max_sy = p -> SizeY;
5816  }
5817  p = (fncMenuItem*)p -> next;
5818  if(p == firstItem) i = VItems;
5819  }
5820  up_obj -> PosY = min_y - ACI_ARROW_OFFS_UP - up_obj -> SizeY;
5821  down_obj -> PosY = max_y + ACI_ARROW_OFFS_DOWN + max_sy;
5822 }
5823 
5824 int fncMenu::change(int x,int y,int mode)
5825 {
5826  fncMenuItem* p;
5827 
5828  x -= PosX;
5829  y -= PosY;
5830 
5831  up_obj -> flags &= ~FM_SELECTED;
5832  down_obj -> flags &= ~FM_SELECTED;
5833 
5834  init_redraw();
5835  if(items -> Size > VItems){
5836  if(x >= 0 && x < SizeX && up_obj -> check_y(y)){
5837  if(!mode)
5838  step_up();
5839  up_obj -> flags |= FM_SELECTED;
5840  set_redraw();
5841  if(prefix) set_prefix(prefix);
5842  init_redraw();
5843  curCount = activeCount;
5844  return 0;
5845  }
5846  if(x >= 0 && x < SizeX && down_obj -> check_y(y)){
5847  if(!mode)
5848  step_down();
5849  down_obj -> flags |= FM_SELECTED;
5850  set_redraw();
5851  if(prefix) set_prefix(prefix);
5852  init_redraw();
5853  curCount = activeCount;
5854  return 0;
5855  }
5856  }
5857  p = (fncMenuItem*)items -> last;
5858  while(p){
5859  if(p -> flags & FM_VISIBLE && p -> check_y(y)){
5860  curItem = p;
5861  curFunction = p -> fnc_code;
5862  if(!mode){
5863  if(!(flags & FM_NO_DEACTIVATE) && !(flags & FM_SUBMENU))
5864  flags &= ~FM_ACTIVE;
5865  if(trigger)
5866  trigger -> press();
5867  }
5868  if(prefix) set_prefix(prefix);
5869  set_redraw();
5870  init_redraw();
5871 
5872  if(flags & FM_SUBMENU){
5873  if(!mode){
5874  aciHandleSubmenuEvent(type,curItem);
5875  if(flags & FM_ITEM_MENU || curFunction == FMENU_OFF){
5876  go2upmenu();
5877  return 1;
5878  }
5879  }
5880  curCount = activeCount;
5881  }
5882  return 1;
5883  }
5884  p = (fncMenuItem*)p -> prev;
5885  }
5886 
5887  if(!mode){
5888  if(flags & FM_SUBMENU){
5889  go2upmenu();
5890  }
5891  }
5892  return 0;
5893 }

5895 void actIntDispatcher::init_submenu(fncMenu* m)
5896 {
5897  char* ptr;
5898 
5899  fncMenu* p = NULL;
5900  aciBitmapMenu* bm = NULL;
5901 
5902  if(!m -> curItem) return;
5903 
5904  if(m -> curItem -> flags & FM_SUBMENU_ITEM){
5905  p = get_menu(m -> curItem -> submenuID);
5906  if(!p) ErrH.Abort("init_submenu() failed...");
5907 
5908  if(m -> curItem -> submenuID == FMENU_TELEPORT_MENU)
5909  p -> curFunction = FMENU_OFF;
5910 
5911  m -> init_submenu(p);
5912  p -> init_curItem();
5913  p -> curCount = p -> activeCount;
5914  p -> flags |= FM_LOCK;
5915 
5916  if(p -> VItems < p -> items -> Size)
5917  p -> firstItem = p -> curItem;
5918  else
5919  p -> firstItem = (fncMenuItem*)p -> items -> first;
5920  }
5921  else {
5922  if(m -> curItem -> flags & FM_BSUBMENU_ITEM){
5923  bm = get_bmenu(m -> curItem -> submenuID);
5924  bm -> upMenu = (iListElement*)m;
5925  if(bm -> activeCount)
5926  bm -> curCount = bm -> activeCount;
5927  }
5928  }
5929 
5930  switch(m -> curFunction){
5931  case FMENU_TARGETS:
5932  if(!p) return;
5933  ptr = GetCompasTarget();
5934  if(!ptr)
5935  p -> curItem = p -> get_obj(aciSTR_OFF);
5936  else
5937  p -> curItem = p -> get_obj(ptr);
5938 
5939  if(p -> VItems < p -> items -> Size)
5940  p -> firstItem = p -> curItem;
5941  else
5942  p -> firstItem = (fncMenuItem*)p -> items -> first;
5943  break;
5944  }
5945 }

5967 void fncMenu::sort(void)
5968 {
5969  int flag = 1;
5970  fncMenuItem* n,*p,*tmp;
5971  while(flag){
5972  flag = 0;
5973  n = (fncMenuItem*)items -> last;
5974  p = (fncMenuItem*)n -> prev;
5975  while(n && p){
5976  if(n -> fnc_code < p -> fnc_code){
5977  items -> swap((iListElement*)n,(iListElement*)p);
5978  tmp = p;
5979  p = n;
5980  n = tmp;
5981  flag = 1;
5982  }
5983  n = p;
5984  if(n)
5985  p = (fncMenuItem*)n -> prev;
5986  }
5987  }
5988 }

6102 void actIntDispatcher::inv_mouse_quant_l(void)
6103 {
6104  int x,y,index;
6105

6107  int my = iMouseY;
6108 
6109  if(flags & AS_ISCREEN) mx += iScreenOffs - 800;
6110 
6111  if(curMatrix && curMatrix -> check_xy(mx,my)){
6112  if(flags & AS_INV_MOVE_ITEM){
6113  x = iMouseX - curMatrix -> ScreenX - (curItem -> ShapeSizeX >> 1) + curItem -> ShapeCenterX;
6114  y = iMouseY - curMatrix -> ScreenY - (curItem -> ShapeSizeY >> 1) + curItem -> ShapeCenterY;
6115 
6116  if(flags & AS_ISCREEN)
6117  x += iScreenOffs - 800;
6118 
6119  y /= aCellSize - (aCellSize >> 2);
6120 
6121  if(y & 0x01) x -= (aCellSize >> 1);
6122  x /= aCellSize;
6123  }
6124  else {
6125  x = iMouseX - curMatrix -> ScreenX;
6126  y = iMouseY - curMatrix -> ScreenY;
6127 
6128  if(flags & AS_ISCREEN)
6129  x += iScreenOffs - 800;
6130

6134  x /= aCellSize;

6137

6143  aciPay4Item(curItem);

6150  SOUND_PICK();
6151  }
6152  }
6153  else {

6155  set_move_item(index);
6156  SOUND_PICK();
6157  }
6158  }
6159  }
6160  }
6161  else {
6162  if(!(flags & AS_ISCREEN)){
6163  if(flags & AS_INV_MOVE_ITEM){
6164  aciSendEvent2itmdsp(ACI_DROP_ITEM,curItem -> item_ptr);
6165  restore_mouse_cursor();
6166  if(curItem -> menu){
6167  remove_menu_item((fncMenu*)curItem -> menu);
6168  }
6169  free_item(curItem);
6170  flags &= ~AS_INV_MOVE_ITEM;
6171  }
6172  }
6173  else {
6174  if(secondMatrix && secondMatrix -> check_xy(mx,my)){
6175  if(flags & AS_INV_MOVE_ITEM){
6176  x = iMouseX - secondMatrix -> ScreenX - (curItem -> ShapeSizeX >> 1) + curItem -> ShapeCenterX;
6177  y = iMouseY - secondMatrix -> ScreenY - (curItem -> ShapeSizeY >> 1) + curItem -> ShapeCenterY;
6178

6180

6189 
6190  x += iScreenOffs - 800;
6191

6193

6195  x /= aCellSize;
6196  }

6447 void actIntDispatcher::change_items(int x,int y,int sflag)
6448 {
6449  actintItemData* d;
6450  int id;
6451 
6452  invMatrix* m = (sflag) ? secondMatrix : curMatrix;
6453 
6454  invItem* p = m -> get_area_item(x,y,curItem);
6455  if(!p) return;
6456 
6457  m -> remove_item(p);
6458  if(!m -> check_fit(x,y,curItem)){
6459  m -> put_item(p -> MatrixX,p -> MatrixY,p);
6460  return;
6461  }
6462  if(flags & AS_ISCREEN && curItem -> flags & INV_ITEM_NO_PAY){

6465  return;
6466  }

6468  }

6470  m -> set_redraw();
6471 
6472  if(!(flags & AS_ISCREEN)){

6474  aciSendEvent2itmdsp(ACI_DEACTIVATE_ITEM,p -> item_ptr);
6475  }

6482  aciSendEvent2itmdsp(ACI_ACTIVATE_ITEM,d,id);
6483  else
6484  aciSendEvent2itmdsp(ACI_DEACTIVATE_ITEM,d);
6485  }
6486  }
6487

6489 
6490  flags |= aMS_MOVED;
6491 
6492  if(!(flags & AS_ISCREEN)){
6493  if(p -> menu)
6494  remove_menu_item((fncMenu*)p -> menu);
6495  if(curItem -> menu)
6496  add_menu_item((fncMenu*)curItem -> menu);
6497  }
6498  else {

6500  ((uvsActInt*)curItem -> uvsDataPtr) -> pos_x = curItem -> MatrixX;
6501  ((uvsActInt*)curItem -> uvsDataPtr) -> pos_y = curItem -> MatrixY;
6502  }
6503  if(p -> uvsDataPtr){
6504  ((uvsActInt*)p -> uvsDataPtr) -> pos_x = -1;
6505  ((uvsActInt*)p -> uvsDataPtr) -> pos_y = -1;
6506 
6507  p -> MatrixX = p -> MatrixY = -1;
6508  }
6509  }
6510 
6511  curItem = p;
6512 
6513  if(iP){
6514  iP -> free_list();
6515  iP -> add_item(curItem->ID_ptr.c_str(),-1,aciCurColorScheme[FM_SELECT_COL]);
6516  if(!(flags & AS_ISCREEN)){
6517  iP -> add_items(curItem -> numComments,curItem -> comments);
6518  if(curItem -> pTemplate)
6519  iP -> add_item(aciGetItemLoad(curItem,0));
6520  }
6521  else {

6523  if(curItem -> pTemplate)
6524  iP -> add_item(aciGetItemLoad(curItem,1));

6526  iP -> add_item(aciGetPrice((iListElement*)curItem,ITEMS_MODE,1));
6527  }

6569 void aIndData::init(void)

6601 
6602  value_ptr[0] = &aciCurArmor;
6603  max_value[0] = &aciMaxArmor;

6607 
6608  colors[0] = ACI_IND_NRG0_COL | (ACI_IND_NRG0_SIZE << 16);
6609  colors[1] = ACI_IND_NRG1_COL | (ACI_IND_NRG1_SIZE << 16);
6610  break;
6611  case IND_JUMP:
6612  value_ptr[0] = &aciCurJumpImpulse;
6613  max_value[0] = &aciMaxJumpImpulse;
6614  colors[0] = ACI_IND_JUMP_COL | (ACI_IND_JUMP_SIZE << 16);
6615  break;
6616  case IND_LOAD:
6617  value_ptr[0] = &aciCurLoad;
6618  max_value[0] = &aciMaxLoad;
6619  colors[0] = ACI_IND_LOAD_COL | (ACI_IND_LOAD_SIZE << 16);
6620  break;
6621  case IND_WPN:
6622  value_ptr[0] = &aciCurWpnResource;

6624  colors[0] = aciCurColorScheme[IND_WPN_COL];
6625  break;

6719 void aIndData::build_pict(void)
6720 {
6721  int ind,v,val,p1,p2,dx,dy,col,col_sz;
6722 
6723  memset(pict_buf,0,SizeX * SizeY);
6724 
6725  if(flags & IND_DISABLED){
6726  dx = (SizeX - aIndBackBML -> SizeX) >> 1;
6727  dy = (SizeY - aIndBackBML -> SizeY) >> 1;
6728  aciPutBufSpr(dx,dy,aIndBackBML -> SizeX,aIndBackBML -> SizeY,SizeX,aIndBackBML -> frames + aIndBackBML -> SizeX * aIndBackBML -> SizeY * (aIndBackBML -> Size - 1),pict_buf,ACI_IND_ARROW_START,ACI_IND_ARROW_SIZE);
6729  }
6730  else {
6731  for(ind = NumVals - 1; ind >= 0; ind --){
6732  p1 = check_points[ind];
6733  p2 = (ind == NumVals - 1) ? 256 : check_points[ind + 1];
6734 
6735  p1 = (p1 * (aIndDataBML -> Size - 1)) >> 8;
6736  p2 = (p2 * (aIndDataBML -> Size - 1)) >> 8;
6737 
6738  value[ind] = *value_ptr[ind];
6739  if(value[ind] >= *max_value[ind]) value[ind] = (*max_value[ind]) - 1;
6740 
6741  if((*max_value[ind]) > 1)
6742  val = (value[ind] * (p2 - p1)) / ((*max_value[ind]) - 1) + p1;
6743  else
6744  val = 0;
6745 
6746  col = colors[ind] & 0xFFFF;
6747  col_sz = (colors[ind] >> 16) & 0xFFFF;
6748 
6749  if(val >= aIndDataBML -> Size) val = aIndDataBML -> Size - 1;
6750  if(val < 0) val = 0;
6751 
6752  if(p2 < 0) p2 = 0;
6753  if(p2 >= aIndDataBML -> Size) p2 = aIndDataBML -> Size - 1;
6754 
6755  dx = (SizeX - aIndDataBML -> SizeX) >> 1;
6756  dy = (SizeY - aIndDataBML -> SizeY) >> 1;
6757 
6758  aciPutBufSpr(dx,dy,aIndDataBML -> SizeX,aIndDataBML -> SizeY,SizeX,aIndDataBML -> frames + aIndDataBML -> SizeX * aIndDataBML -> SizeY * p2,pict_buf,ACI_IND_FON_START,ACI_IND_FON_SIZE);
6759  aciPutBufSpr(dx,dy,aIndDataBML -> SizeX,aIndDataBML -> SizeY,SizeX,aIndDataBML -> frames + aIndDataBML -> SizeX * aIndDataBML -> SizeY * val,pict_buf,col,col_sz);
6760 
6761  aciPutBufSpr(0,0,aIndArrowBML -> SizeX,aIndArrowBML -> SizeY,SizeX,aIndArrowBML -> frames + aIndArrowBML -> SizeX * aIndArrowBML -> SizeY * p2,pict_buf,ACI_IND_ARROW_START,ACI_IND_ARROW_SIZE);
6762  }
6763  aciPutBufSpr(0,0,aIndArrowBML -> SizeX,aIndArrowBML -> SizeY,SizeX,aIndArrowBML -> frames,pict_buf,ACI_IND_ARROW_START,ACI_IND_ARROW_SIZE);
6764 
6765  if(flags & IND_SHOW_VALUES){
6766  for(ind = 0; ind < NumVals; ind ++){
6767  for(v = 0; v < *max_value[ind]; v ++){
6768  if((*max_value[ind]) > 1)
6769  val = (v * aIndArrowBML -> Size) / ((*max_value[ind]) - 1);
6770  else
6771  val = 0;
6772 
6773  if(val < 0) val = 0;
6774  if(val >= aIndArrowBML -> Size) val = aIndArrowBML -> Size - 1;
6775  aciPutBufSpr(0,0,aIndArrowBML -> SizeX,aIndArrowBML -> SizeY,SizeX,aIndArrowBML -> frames + aIndArrowBML -> SizeX * aIndArrowBML -> SizeY * val,pict_buf,ACI_IND_ARROW_START,ACI_IND_ARROW_SIZE);
6776  }
6777  }
6778  }
6779  }
6780 }
6781 
6782 void aIndData::redraw(int dx,int dy)
6783 {
6784  int i,x,y;
6785  for(i = 0; i < NumVals; i ++){
6786  if(*value_ptr[i] != value[i]){
6787  build_pict();
6788  i = NumVals;
6789  }
6790  }
6791  if(dx == -1){
6792  XGR_PutSpr(PosX,PosY,SizeX,SizeY,pict_buf,XGR_HIDDEN_FON);
6793  if(bml) bml -> show();
6794  }
6795  else {
6796  switch(CornerNum){
6797  case IND_UP_LEFT:
6798  x = dx;
6799  y = dy;
6800  break;
6801  case IND_UP_RIGHT:
6802  x = XGR_MAXX - dx - SizeX;
6803  y = dy;
6804  break;
6805  case IND_DN_RIGHT:
6806  x = XGR_MAXX - dx - SizeX;
6807  y = XGR_MAXY - dy - SizeY;
6808  break;
6809  case IND_DN_LEFT:
6810  x = dx;
6811  y = XGR_MAXY - dy - SizeY;
6812  break;
6813  }
6814  XGR_PutSpr(x,y,SizeX,SizeY,pict_buf,XGR_HIDDEN_FON);
6815  }
6816 }

6818 void actIntDispatcher::init_inds(void)
6819 {
6820  int lx,ly,rx,ry,cx,cy;
6821  ibsObject* ibs = curIbs;
6822  XGR_MousePromptData* pr;
6823 
6824  lx = ibs -> PosX;
6825  ly = ibs -> PosY;
6826 
6827  rx = lx + ibs -> SizeX;
6828  ry = ly + ibs -> SizeY;
6829 
6830  aIndData* p = (aIndData*)indList -> last;
6831  while(p){
6832  switch(p -> CornerNum){
6833  case IND_UP_LEFT:
6834  p -> PosX = lx + ibs -> indPosX[0];
6835  p -> PosY = ly + ibs -> indPosY[0];
6836  break;
6837  case IND_UP_RIGHT:
6838  p -> PosX = rx - ibs -> indPosX[1] - p -> SizeX;
6839  p -> PosY = ly + ibs -> indPosY[1];
6840  break;
6841  case IND_DN_LEFT:
6842  p -> PosX = lx + ibs -> indPosX[2];
6843  p -> PosY = ry - ibs -> indPosY[2] - p -> SizeY;
6844  break;
6845  case IND_DN_RIGHT:
6846  p -> PosX = rx - ibs -> indPosX[3] - p -> SizeX;
6847  p -> PosY = ry - ibs -> indPosY[3] - p -> SizeY;
6848  break;
6849  }
6850  if(p -> bml){
6851  cx = p -> PosX + (p -> SizeX >> 1);
6852  cy = p -> PosY + (p -> SizeY >> 1);
6853  p -> bml -> OffsX = cx - (p -> bml -> SizeX >> 1);
6854  p -> bml -> OffsY = cy - (p -> bml -> SizeY >> 1);
6855  }
6856  if(p -> ID == IND_DVC){
6857  if(curMatrix && !curMatrix -> slot_exist(3)){
6858  p -> flags |= IND_DISABLED;
6859  }
6860  else {
6861  p -> flags &= ~IND_DISABLED;
6862  }
6863  }
6864  pr = invPrompt -> getData(p -> ID);
6865  if(pr){
6866  if(p -> flags & IND_DISABLED){
6867  pr -> StartX = 0;
6868  pr -> StartY = 0;
6869 
6870  pr -> SizeX = 0;
6871  pr -> SizeY = 0;
6872  }
6873  else {
6874  pr -> StartX = p -> PosX;
6875  pr -> StartY = p -> PosY;
6876 
6877  pr -> SizeX = p -> SizeX;
6878  pr -> SizeY = p -> SizeY;
6879  }
6880  }
6881  pr = infPrompt -> getData(p -> ID);
6882  if(pr){
6883  if(p -> flags & IND_DISABLED){
6884  pr -> StartX = 0;
6885  pr -> StartY = 0;
6886 
6887  pr -> SizeX = 0;
6888  pr -> SizeY = 0;
6889  }
6890  else {
6891  pr -> StartX = p -> PosX;
6892  pr -> StartY = p -> PosY;
6893 
6894  pr -> SizeX = p -> SizeX;
6895  pr -> SizeY = p -> SizeY;
6896  }
6897  }
6898  p = (aIndData*)p -> prev;
6899  }
6900 }
6901 
6902 void invItem::calc_shape_center(void)
6903 {
6904  int i,x,y,min_x,min_y,max_x,max_y;
6905  int cell_sz,cell_sz2,cell_sz4;
6906 
6907  int* tmpShapeX;
6908  int* tmpShapeY;
6909 
6910  x = y = 0;
6911  min_x = min_y = max_x = max_y = 0;
6912 
6913  cell_sz = aCellSize;
6914  cell_sz2 = aCellSize/2;
6915  cell_sz4 = aCellSize/4;
6916 
6917  if(ShapeLen){
6918  tmpShapeX = new int[ShapeLen];
6919  tmpShapeY = new int[ShapeLen];
6920 
6921  for(i = 0; i < ShapeLen; i ++){
6922  tmpShapeX[i] = ShapeX[i] * 2;
6923  tmpShapeY[i] = ShapeY[i];
6924 
6925  if(ShapeY[i] & 1)
6926  tmpShapeX[i] ++;
6927 
6928  x = tmpShapeX[i];
6929  y = tmpShapeY[i];
6930 
6931  if(x < min_x){
6932  min_x = x;
6933  }
6934  if(y < min_y){
6935  min_y = y;
6936  }
6937 
6938  if(x > max_x){
6939  max_x = x;
6940  }
6941  if(y > max_y){
6942  max_y = y;
6943  }
6944  }
6945  for(i = 0; i < ShapeLen; i ++){
6946  tmpShapeX[i] -= min_x;
6947  tmpShapeY[i] -= min_y;
6948  }
6949  }
6950 
6951  ShapeSizeX = cell_sz + (max_x - min_x) * cell_sz2;
6952  ShapeSizeY = cell_sz + (max_y - min_y) * (cell_sz - cell_sz4);
6953 
6954  if(ShapeLen){
6955  ShapeCenterX = (tmpShapeX[0] + 1) * cell_sz2;
6956  ShapeCenterY = tmpShapeY[0] * (cell_sz - cell_sz4) + cell_sz2;
6957 
6958  delete[] tmpShapeX;
6959  delete[] tmpShapeY;
6960  }

7006 #if defined(_GENERATE_MATRIX_SHAPES_) || defined(_GENERATE_iMATRIX_SHAPES_)
7007 void invMatrix::generate_shape(void)
7008 {

7019

7026  XBuf <= internalID < ".bmp";
7027

7030  }
7031 
7032  buf = new unsigned char[ssz];
7033  memset(buf,0,ssz);

7036  int dx2 = aCellSize >> 1;
7037  int dx4 = aCellSize >> 2;
7038 
7039  unsigned char* p;

7041

7043  if(i & 0x01){
7044  x += dx2;
7045  }

7072  swap_buf_col(i + 83,SHAPE_DEPTH,ssx,ssy,buf);

7075  fh < (short)ssx < (short)ssy;
7076  fh.write(buf,ssz);
7077  fh.close();

7082  XBuf <= internalID < ".shp";

7086

7524  }
7525  if(pr0){
7526  pr0 -> StartX = 0;
7527  pr0 -> StartY = 0;
7528 
7529  pr0 -> SizeX = 0;
7530  pr0 -> SizeY = 0;
7531  }
7532  }
7533  }
7534 
7535  if(flags & aMS_MOVED){
7536  if(curMatrix) curMatrix -> clear_shadow_cells();
7537  if(secondMatrix) secondMatrix -> clear_shadow_cells();
7538  }
7539 
7540  mx = iMouseX;
7541  my = iMouseY;
7542 
7543  if(flags & AS_ISCREEN)
7544  mx += iScreenOffs - 800;
7545 
7546  if(flags & AS_INV_MOVE_ITEM){
7547  if(curItem -> flags & INV_ITEM_NO_PAY && ((uvsActInt*)curItem -> uvsDataPtr) -> price > cr){
7548  if(!pr){
7549  pr = new XGR_MousePromptData;
7550  pr -> ID = ACI_NO_CASH_PROMPT;
7551  XGR_MouseObj.promptData -> AddElement((XListElement*)pr);
7552  pr -> set_text(aciSTR_NO_CASH);
7553  }
7554  pr -> StartX = curMatrix -> ScreenX + iScreenOffs;
7555  pr -> StartY = curMatrix -> ScreenY;
7556 
7557  pr -> SizeX = curMatrix -> ScreenSizeX;
7558  pr -> SizeY = curMatrix -> ScreenSizeY;
7559  }
7560  }
7561 
7562  if(curMatrix && curMatrix -> check_xy(mx,my)){
7563  if(flags & AS_INV_MOVE_ITEM){
7564  x = iMouseX - curMatrix -> ScreenX - (curItem -> ShapeSizeX >> 1) + curItem -> ShapeCenterX;
7565  y = iMouseY - curMatrix -> ScreenY - (curItem -> ShapeSizeY >> 1) + curItem -> ShapeCenterY;
7566 
7567  x += iScreenOffs - 800;
7568 
7569  y /= aCellSize - (aCellSize >> 2);
7570 
7571  if(y & 0x01) x -= (aCellSize >> 1);
7572  x /= aCellSize;
7573  }
7574  else {
7575  x = iMouseX - curMatrix -> ScreenX;
7576  y = iMouseY - curMatrix -> ScreenY;
7577 
7578  x += iScreenOffs - 800;
7579 
7580  y /= aCellSize - (aCellSize >> 2);
7581 
7582  if(y & 0x01) x -= (aCellSize >> 1);
7583  x /= aCellSize;
7584  }
7585 
7586  if(x >= 0 && x < curMatrix -> SizeX && y >= 0 && y < curMatrix -> SizeY){
7587  if(flags & AS_INV_MOVE_ITEM){
7588  if(curMatrix -> check_fit(x,y,curItem)){
7589  curMatrix -> put_item_shadow(x,y,curItem);
7590  }
7591  else {
7592  p = curMatrix -> get_area_item(x,y,curItem);
7593  if(p){
7594  curMatrix -> remove_item(p,1);
7595  if(curMatrix -> check_fit(x,y,curItem))
7596  curMatrix -> put_item_shadow(x,y,curItem);
7597  curMatrix -> put_item(p -> MatrixX,p -> MatrixY,p,1);
7598  }
7599  }
7600  }
7601  else {
7602  if(iP){
7603  p = curMatrix -> get_item(x,y);
7604  if(iP -> items -> Size){
7605  iP -> free_list();
7606  iP -> set_redraw();
7607  }
7608  if(p){
7609  p1 = get_iitem(p -> ID);
7610  iP -> add_item(p1->ID_ptr.c_str(),-1,aciCurColorScheme[FM_SELECT_COL]);
7611  iP -> add_items(p1 -> numComments,p1 -> comments);
7612  if(p1 -> pTemplate)
7613  iP -> add_item(aciGetItemLoad(p,1));
7614  if(!uvsCurrentWorldUnable)
7615  iP -> add_item(aciGetPrice((iListElement*)p,ITEMS_MODE,1));
7616  }
7617  }
7618  }
7619  }
7620  }
7621  else {
7622  if(secondMatrix && secondMatrix -> check_xy(mx,my)){
7623  if(flags & AS_INV_MOVE_ITEM){
7624  x = iMouseX - secondMatrix -> ScreenX - (curItem -> ShapeSizeX >> 1) + curItem -> ShapeCenterX;
7625  y = iMouseY - secondMatrix -> ScreenY - (curItem -> ShapeSizeY >> 1) + curItem -> ShapeCenterY;
7626 
7627  x += iScreenOffs - 800;
7628 
7629  y /= aCellSize - (aCellSize >> 2);
7630 
7631  if(y & 0x01) x -= (aCellSize >> 1);
7632  x /= aCellSize;
7633  }
7634  else {
7635  x = iMouseX - secondMatrix -> ScreenX;
7636  y = iMouseY - secondMatrix -> ScreenY;
7637 
7638  x += iScreenOffs - 800;
7639 
7640  y /= aCellSize - (aCellSize >> 2);
7641 
7642  if(y & 0x01) x -= (aCellSize >> 1);
7643  x /= aCellSize;
7644  }
7645 
7646  if(x >= 0 && x < secondMatrix -> SizeX && y >= 0 && y < secondMatrix -> SizeY){
7647  if(flags & AS_INV_MOVE_ITEM){
7648  if(secondMatrix -> check_fit(x,y,curItem)){
7649  secondMatrix -> put_item_shadow(x,y,curItem);
7650  }
7651  else {
7652  p = secondMatrix -> get_area_item(x,y,curItem);
7653  if(p){
7654  secondMatrix -> remove_item(p,1);
7655  if(secondMatrix -> check_fit(x,y,curItem))
7656  secondMatrix -> put_item_shadow(x,y,curItem);
7657  secondMatrix -> put_item(p -> MatrixX,p -> MatrixY,p,1);
7658  }
7659  }
7660  }
7661  else {
7662  if(iP){
7663  p = secondMatrix -> get_item(x,y);
7664  if(iP -> items -> Size){
7665  iP -> free_list();
7666  iP -> set_redraw();
7667  }
7668  if(p){
7669  iP -> add_item(p->ID_ptr.c_str(),-1,aciCurColorScheme[FM_SELECT_COL]);
7670  iP -> add_items(p -> numComments,p -> comments);
7671  if(p -> pTemplate)
7672  iP -> add_item(aciGetItemLoad(p,1));
7673  if(!uvsCurrentWorldUnable)
7674  iP -> add_item(aciGetPrice((iListElement*)p,ITEMS_MODE,1));
7675  }
7676  }
7677  }
7678  }
7679  }
7680  else {
7681  if(!(flags & AS_INV_MOVE_ITEM)){
7682  if(iP){
7683  if(iP -> items -> Size){
7684  iP -> free_list();
7685  iP -> set_redraw();
7686  }
7687  }
7688  }
7689  }
7690  }
7691 
7692  if(flags & aMS_MOVED){
7693  if(curMatrix && curMatrix -> check_redraw()){
7694  curMatrix -> flags |= IM_REDRAW_SHADOW;
7695  }
7696  if(secondMatrix && secondMatrix -> check_redraw()){
7697  secondMatrix -> flags |= IM_REDRAW_SHADOW;
7698  }
7699  }
7700  if(iP){
7701  if(!iP -> items -> Size){
7702  aciInitMechosInfo(curMatrix,iP);
7703  }
7704  }
7705 }

7707 int invMatrix::check_redraw(void)
7708 {
7709  int i,j,index = 0;
7710  for(i = 0; i < SizeY; i ++){
7711  for(j = 0; j < SizeX; j ++){
7712  if(matrix[index] -> flags & (AS_IN_SHADOW | AS_REDRAW_CELL))
7713  return 1;
7714  index ++;
7715  }
7716  }
7717  return 0;
7718 }

7746 void actIntDispatcher::trade_items(invMatrix* p,int imode)
7747 {
7748  int cnt = 1,x,y,fl;
7749  invItem* it,*it1,*itm;
7750 
7751  it = (invItem*)curMatrix -> items -> last;
7752  while(it){
7753  it1 = (invItem*)it -> prev;
7754 
7755  cnt = it -> dropCount;
7756  x = it -> MatrixX;
7757  y = it -> MatrixY;
7758  fl = it -> flags;
7759 
7760  curMatrix -> remove_item(it,1);
7761 
7762  if(imode)
7763  itm = get_iitem(it -> ID);
7764  else
7765  itm = get_item(it -> ID);
7766 
7767  if(!itm)
7768  ErrH.Abort("Bad item ptr...");
7769 
7770  itm -> clone(it);
7771  if(!p -> put_item(x,y,it,1))
7772  ErrH.Abort("Bad trade item...");
7773 
7774  it -> dropCount = cnt;
7775  it -> flags = fl;
7776  it = it1;
7777  }
7778 }

7891  t -> uvsDataPtr = itm -> uvsDataPtr;
7892  p -> put_item(itm -> MatrixX,itm -> MatrixY,t,1);
7893  itm = (invItem*)itm -> prev;
7894  }

8012 void aciWorldMap::calc_shapes(void)
8013 {
8014  int i;
8015  XStream fh;
8016  if(!ShapeSizeX) ShapeSizeX = new short[3];
8017  if(!ShapeSizeY) ShapeSizeY = new short[3];
8018  if(!shapes){
8019  shapes = new unsigned char*[3];
8020  for(i = 0; i < 3; i ++){
8021  if(!shape_files[i]) ErrH.Abort("Map shape file not found...");
8022 
8023  fh.open(shape_files[i]);
8024  fh > ShapeSizeX[i] > ShapeSizeY[i];
8025  shapes[i] = new unsigned char[ShapeSizeX[i] * ShapeSizeY[i]];
8026  fh.read(shapes[i],ShapeSizeX[i] * ShapeSizeY[i]);
8027  fh.close();
8028  }
8029  }

8051 #define WORLD_COORD_MAX 1000
8052 void aciWorldMap::remap_coords(void)
8053 {
8054  int x,y;
8055  aciWorldInfo* p = (aciWorldInfo*)world_list -> last;
8056  if(flags & WMAP_REMAP_COORDS)
8057  return;
8058  while(p){
8059  x = (p -> PosX * SizeX) / WORLD_COORD_MAX;
8060  y = (p -> PosY * SizeY) / WORLD_COORD_MAX;
8061 
8062  p -> PosX = x;
8063  p -> PosY = y;
8064 
8065  p = (aciWorldInfo*)p -> prev;
8066  }
8067  JumpCountSizeX = (JUMP_SIZE_X * SizeX) / WORLD_COORD_MAX;
8068  JumpCountSizeY = (JUMP_SIZE_Y * SizeY) / WORLD_COORD_MAX;
8069 
8070  JumpCountX = (SizeX - JumpCountSizeX) / 2;
8071  JumpCountY = (JUMP_Y * SizeY) / WORLD_COORD_MAX;
8072 
8073  flags |= WMAP_REMAP_COORDS;
8074 }

8076 //TODO need fast malloc
8077 void aciWorldInfo::redraw(int bsx,int bsy,unsigned char* buf)
8078 {
8079  int x,y,sx,sy,ox,oy;
8080  int border_col = 0,floor_col = 0;
8081 
8082  unsigned char* shape,*shape1;
8083  aciWorldMap* p = (aciWorldMap*)owner;
8084 
8085  if(flags & AS_SECRET_WORLD && !(flags & AS_VISIBLE_WORLD))
8086  return;
8087 
8088  floor_col = aciCurColorScheme[ACI_BACK_COL];
8089 
8090  if(flags & AS_VISIBLE_WORLD){
8091  border_col = aciCurColorScheme[WORLD_BORDER_VIS_COL];
8092  floor_col = aciCurColorScheme[WORLD_VISIBLE_COL];
8093  }
8094  if(flags & AS_SPECIAL_WORLD){
8095  border_col = aciCurColorScheme[WORLD_BORDER_SPC_COL];
8096  floor_col = aciCurColorScheme[WORLD_SPECIAL_COL];
8097  }
8098  if(flags & AS_EXPLORED_WORLD){
8099  border_col = aciCurColorScheme[WORLD_BORDER_EXP_COL];
8100  floor_col = aciCurColorScheme[WORLD_EXPLORED_COL];
8101  }
8102  if(flags & AS_CURRENT_WORLD){
8103  border_col = aciCurColorScheme[WORLD_BORDER_CUR_COL];
8104  floor_col = aciCurColorScheme[WORLD_CURRENT_COL];
8105  }
8106 // if(flags & AS_ACCESSIBLE_WORLD){
8107 // border_col = aciCurColorScheme[WORLD_BORDER_ACC_COL];
8108 // floor_col = aciCurColorScheme[WORLD_ACCESSIBLE_COL];
8109 // }
8110 
8111  sx = p -> ShapeSizeX[shape_id];
8112  sy = p -> ShapeSizeY[shape_id];
8113  shape = p -> shapes[shape_id];
8114 
8115  ox = p -> ShapeOffsX[shape_id];
8116  oy = p -> ShapeOffsY[shape_id];
8117 
8118  shape1 = new unsigned char[sx * sy];
8119  memcpy(shape1,shape,sx * sy);
8120 
8121  x = PosX - sx/2;
8122  y = PosY - sy/2;
8123 
8124  swap_buf_col(2,border_col,sx,sy,shape1);
8125  swap_buf_col(1,floor_col,sx,sy,shape1);
8126  mem_putspr(x,y,sx,sy,bsx,bsy,shape1,buf);
8127 
8128  x = PosX - (aScrFonts[font] -> SizeX >> 1) + ox;
8129  y = PosY - (aScrFonts[font] -> SizeY >> 1) + oy;
8130 
8131  aPutChar(x,y,font,border_col,letter,bsx,bsy,buf);
8132  delete[] shape1;
8133 }

8192 void actIntDispatcher::swap_matrices(void)
8193 {

8198  v = aciGetCurCredits();

8301 void actIntDispatcher::put_in_slot(actintItemData* d)
8302 {
8303  int x,y,index = 0,px,py,id;
8304  int ms_flag = 0;
8305  invItem* dvc;
8306  invItem* p = (invItem*)d -> actintOwner;
8307 
8308  //std::cout<<"actIntDispatcher::put_in_slot "<<p->fname<<std::endl;
8309 
8310  if(flags & AS_INV_MOVE_ITEM && curItem == p){
8311  ms_flag = 1;
8312  }
8313  else {
8314  id = curMatrix -> get_item_slot(p);
8315  if(id == AS_DEVICE_SLOT) return;
8316  }
8317 
8318  for(y = 0; y < curMatrix -> SizeY; y ++){
8319  for(x = 0; x < curMatrix -> SizeX; x ++){
8320  if(curMatrix -> matrix[index] -> slotType == AS_DEVICE_SLOT){
8321  if(curMatrix -> check_fit(x,y,p)){
8322  if(!ms_flag){
8323  curMatrix -> remove_item(p);
8324  }
8325  else {
8326  flags ^= AS_INV_MOVE_ITEM;
8327  restore_mouse_cursor();
8328  curMatrix -> clear_shadow_cells();
8329  curItem = NULL;
8330  if(iP){
8331  iP -> free_list();
8332  iP -> set_redraw();
8333  }
8334  }
8335  curMatrix -> put_item(x,y,p);
8336  SOUND_DROP();
8337  id = curMatrix -> get_item_slot(p);
8338  aciSendEvent2itmdsp(ACI_ACTIVATE_ITEM,d,id);
8339  if(curMode == AS_INV_MODE)
8340  curMatrix -> set_redraw();
8341  return;
8342  }
8343  else {
8344  dvc = curMatrix -> get_area_item(x,y,p);
8345  if(dvc){
8346  curMatrix -> remove_item(dvc);
8347  if(!curMatrix -> check_fit(x,y,p)){
8348  curMatrix -> put_item(dvc -> MatrixX,dvc -> MatrixY,dvc);
8349  return;
8350  }
8351  if(!curMatrix -> check_fit(x,y,p)) ErrH.Abort("put_in_slot() failed...");
8352  if(!ms_flag){
8353  px = p -> MatrixX;
8354  py = p -> MatrixY;
8355  curMatrix -> remove_item(p);
8356  curMatrix -> put_item(dvc -> MatrixX,dvc -> MatrixY,p);
8357  curMatrix -> put_item(px,py,dvc);
8358  SOUND_DROP();
8359  }
8360  else {
8361  curMatrix -> put_item(dvc -> MatrixX,dvc -> MatrixY,p);
8362  SOUND_DROP();
8363  curItem = dvc;
8364  if(iP){
8365  iP -> free_list();
8366  iP -> add_item(curItem->ID_ptr.c_str(),-1,aciCurColorScheme[FM_SELECT_COL]);
8367  iP -> add_items(curItem -> numComments,curItem -> comments);
8368  if(curItem -> pTemplate)
8369  iP -> add_item(aciGetItemLoad(curItem,0));
8370  iP -> set_redraw();
8371  }
8372  set_mouse_cursor(dvc -> frame,dvc -> ScreenSizeX,dvc -> ScreenSizeY);
8373  }
8374 
8375  aciSendEvent2itmdsp(ACI_DEACTIVATE_ITEM,dvc -> item_ptr);
8376 
8377  id = curMatrix -> get_item_slot(p);
8378  aciSendEvent2itmdsp(ACI_ACTIVATE_ITEM,d,id);
8379 
8380  if(curMode == AS_INV_MODE)
8381  curMatrix -> set_redraw();
8382  return;
8383  }
8384  }
8385  }
8386  index ++;
8387  }
8388  }
8389 }

8506 const int aciSaveVersion = 1;
8507 
8508 void actIntDispatcher::save_data(XStream* fh)
8509 {
8510  invItem* p;
8511  aciWorldInfo* w;
8512 
8513  int cr = aciGetCurCredits();
8514 
8515  *fh < aciSaveVersion;
8516 
8517  if(curMatrix){
8518  *fh < curMatrix -> type < curMatrix -> items -> Size;
8519  p = (invItem*)curMatrix -> items -> last;
8520  while(p){
8521  *fh < p -> ID < p -> MatrixX < p -> MatrixY < p -> dropCount;
8522  p = (invItem*)p -> prev;
8523  }
8524  }
8525  else {
8526  *fh < (int)(-1);
8527  }
8528  *fh < cr;
8529  if(wMap){
8530  w = (aciWorldInfo*)wMap -> world_list -> last;
8531  while(w){
8532  *fh < w -> flags;
8533  w = (aciWorldInfo*)w -> prev;
8534  }
8535  w = (aciWorldInfo*)wMap -> world_list -> last;
8536  while(w){
8537  fh -> write(w -> links,AS_MAX_WORLD);
8538  w = (aciWorldInfo*)w -> prev;
8539  }
8540  }
8541 }
8542 
8543 void actIntDispatcher::load_data(XStream* fh)
8544 {
8545  int i,n,x,y,d,itm_size,ver,cr;
8546 
8547  *fh > ver;
8548 
8549  if(ver < 0 || ver > aciSaveVersion) ErrH.Abort("Bad save version...");
8550 
8551  aciWorldInfo* w;
8552  invItem* p,*p1;
8553  invMatrix* m;
8554  if(curMatrix)
8555  free_matrix(curMatrix);
8556 
8557  *fh > n > itm_size;
8558  if(n != -1){
8559  curMatrix = alloc_matrix(n);
8560  if(flags & AS_ISCREEN)
8561  m = get_imatrix(n);
8562  else
8563  m = get_matrix(n);
8564 
8565  m -> clone(curMatrix);
8566  for(i = 0; i < itm_size; i ++){
8567  *fh > n > x > y > d;
8568  if(flags & AS_ISCREEN)
8569  p = get_iitem(n);
8570  else
8571  p = get_item(n);
8572 
8573  p1 = alloc_item();
8574  p -> clone(p1);
8575  curMatrix -> put_item(x,y,p1,1);
8576  p1 -> dropCount = d;
8577  }
8578  }
8579  else {
8580  curMatrix = NULL;
8581  }
8582  *fh > cr;
8583  aciUpdateCurCredits(cr);
8584 
8585  if(wMap){
8586  w = (aciWorldInfo*)wMap -> world_list -> last;
8587  while(w){
8588  *fh > w -> flags;
8589  w = (aciWorldInfo*)w -> prev;
8590  }
8591  w = (aciWorldInfo*)wMap -> world_list -> last;
8592  while(w){
8593  fh -> read(w -> links,AS_MAX_WORLD);
8594  w = (aciWorldInfo*)w -> prev;
8595  }
8596  }
8597 }

8599 void actIntDispatcher::aml_check_redraw(int x,int y)

8602  InfoPanel* pl;
8603 
8604  y += 16;
8605 
8606  pl = (InfoPanel*)i_infoPanels -> last;

8609  x1 = pl -> PosX + pl -> SizeX/2;

8613  dy = pl -> SizeY/2 + aciML_ToolzerRadius * 2;

8624  dy = qMenu -> ScreenSizeY/2 + aciML_ToolzerRadius;
8625

8627  }

8728  if(dx){

8730  for(i = 0; i < items -> Size; i ++){
8731  m -> PosX += dx;
8732  m = (fncMenu*)m -> next;
8733  }

8754 
8755 void fncMenuSet::redraw(void)
8756 {
8757  int i,y,sx,dx,rdx,index,r_index;
8758 
8759  fncMenu* m;
8760  iScreenObject* obj;
8761 
8762  if(!(data -> flags & EL_DATA_LOADED))
8763  return;
8764 
8765  obj = (iScreenObject*)data -> owner;
8766  obj -> flags |= (OBJ_MUST_REDRAW | OBJ_CLEAR_FON);
8767 
8768  if(!redraw_data || !(redraw_data -> flags & EL_DATA_LOADED)){
8769  memset(data -> fdata,0,data -> SizeX * data -> SizeY);
8770  return;
8771  }
8772 
8773 // memset(redraw_data -> fdata,4,redraw_data -> SizeX * redraw_data -> SizeY);
8774  memset(redraw_data -> fdata,0,redraw_data -> SizeX * redraw_data -> SizeY);
8775  m = (fncMenu*)items -> first;
8776  for(i = 0; i < items -> Size; i ++){
8777  m -> redraw();
8778  m = (fncMenu*)m -> next;
8779  }
8780  if(data -> SizeX > redraw_data -> SizeX){
8781  sx = redraw_data -> SizeX;
8782  dx = (data -> SizeX - sx)/2;
8783  rdx = 0;
8784  }
8785  else {
8786  sx = data -> SizeX;
8787  dx = 0;
8788  rdx = -PosX;
8789 // rdx = (redraw_data -> SizeX - sx)/2 - PosX;
8790  }
8791 
8792  index = dx;
8793  r_index = rdx;
8794  for(y = 0; y < data -> SizeY; y ++){
8795  memcpy(data -> fdata + index,redraw_data -> fdata + r_index,sx);
8796  index += data -> SizeX;
8797  r_index += redraw_data -> SizeX;
8798  }
8799 
8800  flags &= ~FMC_REDRAW;
8801 }

8837 void fncMenuSet::key_trap(int x,int y)
8838 {
8839  int flag = 0,fnc;
8840  fncMenu* m;
8841  if(!check_xy(x,y)) return;
8842 
8843  x -= ScreenX + PosX;
8844  y -= ScreenY;
8845 
8846  m = (fncMenu*)items -> last;
8847  while(m){
8848  if(m -> items -> Size > 1){
8849  fnc = m -> curFunction;
8850  m -> change(x,y);
8851  if(fnc != m -> curFunction)

9135 int aciLocationShutterInfo::Quant(void)
9136 {
9137  if(curDelta.X){
9138  if(curDelta.X < 0){
9139  if(curPos.X > trgPos.X){
9140  curPos.X += curDelta.X;
9141  if(curPos.X <= trgPos.X)
9142  curPos.X = trgPos.X;
9143  }
9144  }
9145  else {
9146  if(curPos.X < trgPos.X){
9147  curPos.X += curDelta.X;
9148  if(curPos.X >= trgPos.X)
9149  curPos.X = trgPos.X;
9150  }
9151  }
9152  }
9153  if(curDelta.Y){
9154  if(curDelta.Y < 0){
9155  if(curPos.Y > trgPos.Y){
9156  curPos.Y += curDelta.Y;
9157  if(curPos.Y <= trgPos.Y)
9158  curPos.Y = trgPos.Y;
9159  }
9160  }
9161  else {
9162  if(curPos.Y < trgPos.Y){
9163  curPos.Y += curDelta.Y;
9164  if(curPos.Y >= trgPos.Y)
9165  curPos.Y = trgPos.Y;
9166  }
9167  }
9168  }
9169  if(curPos.X == trgPos.X && curPos.Y == trgPos.Y) return 1;
9170  return 0;
9171 }

9497 void aciScreenText::alloc(char* ptr,int sz)
9498 {
9499  free();

9501  memcpy(data,ptr,sz);
9502  data[sz] = '\n';
9503  dataSize = sz + 1;
9504

9506 
9507  prepare();

9509  flags |= ACI_TEXT_INIT;

9512 
9513 void aciScreenText::prepare(void)
9514 {
9515  int i,j,cur_str,start_str,cur_text_str;
9516  char* strStart;
9517  aciScreenTextString* s;
9518  aciScreenTextPage* p;
9519 
9520  strStart = data;
9521  start_str = cur_str = cur_text_str = 0;
9522  for(i = 0; i < dataSize; i ++){
9523  if(data[i] == '\\' && i < (dataSize - 1) && data[i + 1] == '\\'){
9524  cur_text_str = MaxPageStr;
9525  data[i] = 0;
9526  data[i + 1] = 0;
9527  while(i < (dataSize - 1) && data[i] != '\n') i ++;
9528  }
9529  if(data[i] == '\n'){
9530  data[i] = 0;
9531  s = new aciScreenTextString;
9532  s -> data = strStart;
9533  StrTable -> connect((iListElement*)s);
9534  if(i < (dataSize - 1)) strStart = data + i + 1;
9535 
9536  cur_text_str ++;
9537  cur_str ++;
9538  }
9539  if(cur_text_str >= MaxPageStr){
9540  p = new aciScreenTextPage;
9541  p -> StartStr = start_str;
9542  p -> NumStr = cur_str - start_str + 1;
9543  if(p -> NumStr)
9544  p -> StrTable = new char*[p -> NumStr];
9545  PageTable -> connect((iListElement*)p);
9546 
9547  start_str = cur_str;
9548  cur_text_str = 0;
9549  }
9550  }
9551  if(cur_text_str){
9552  p = new aciScreenTextPage;
9553  p -> StartStr = start_str;
9554  p -> NumStr = cur_str - start_str + 1;
9555  if(p -> NumStr)
9556  p -> StrTable = new char*[p -> NumStr];
9557  PageTable -> connect((iListElement*)p);
9558 
9559  start_str = cur_str + 1;
9560  cur_text_str = 0;
9561  }
9562  p = (aciScreenTextPage*)PageTable -> first;
9563  for(i = 0; i < PageTable -> Size; i ++){
9564  s = (aciScreenTextString*)StrTable -> first;
9565  for(j = 0; j < p -> StartStr; j ++){
9566  s = (aciScreenTextString*)s -> next;
9567  }
9568  for(j = 0; j < p -> NumStr; j ++){
9569  p -> StrTable[j] = s -> data;
9570  s = (aciScreenTextString*)s -> next;
9571  }
9572  p = (aciScreenTextPage*)p -> next;
9573  }
9574  for(i = 0; i < dataSize; i ++)
9575  if(data[i] == '\r') data[i] = 0;
9576 }

9578 void aciScreenText::redraw(void)
9579 {
9580  int i,x,y;
9581  aciScreenTextPage* p;
9582  char* str;
9583 
9584  if(flags & ACI_TEXT_END) return;
9585 
9586  p = (aciScreenTextPage*)PageTable -> first;
9587  for(i = 0; i < CurPage; i ++){
9588  p = (aciScreenTextPage*)p -> next;
9589  }
9590 
9591  y = (XGR_MAXY - (DeltaY + aTextHeight32((void *)"",font,1)) * p -> NumStr)/2;
9592  for(i = 0; i < CurStr; i ++){
9593  str = p -> StrTable[i];
9594  x = (XGR_MAXX - aTextWidth32(str,font,1))/2;
9595 
9596  aOutText32(x,y,color,str,font,1,1);
9597  y += DeltaY + aTextHeight32(str,font,1);
9598  }
9599  CurPageData = p;
9600 }

9608  CurStr ++;
9609  }
9610  else
9611  flags |= ACI_TEXT_REDRAW;
9612 
9613  Timer = 0;
9614  }
9615 }
